  dialogueHidesSubmit: 0
  lines:
  - 'Faction Member: You remember those rumours I was talking about? '
  - 'Faction Member: The whole shit about the illness being part of some plan, I
    got some dirt on the whole thing, here.'
  - (Cult Plan Component Document)
  - "Faction Member: We\u2019re thinking this entire town and society being cultivated
    is another part of their plan, the scope of this whole thing seems to be insane. "
  - 'Faction Member: You might be an even bigger pawn than I initially thought.'
  - 'Father: Do you want your own family though? One you made yourself?'
  - "Faction Member:  You able to read a character whatsoever? I can\u2019t stand
    any of that bullshit that them and everyone else keeps bushing. Even if I did,
    not a chance you\u2019d find anyone in here  who\u2019d want to be a part of
    that family, so what\u2019s theres no point in even bothering."
  - "Faction Member:  Anyways, that\u2019s all I\u2019ve got for now, I\u2019ll get
    back to you later."
